      <head>Hotel Bristol</head>
      <div>

        <p>Hotel in Vienna, situated on the K&#xE4;rntner Ring next to the Vienna State Opera.
          Opened in 1892, it was an elegant focal point for the rich cultural and business life of
          the city.</p>
        
        <p>It was <ref cRef="dalbert_eugen">Eugen d'Albert</ref>'s usual residence when in Vienna, and Schenker received many
          letters from him with the Hotel Bristol's distinctive Jugendstil letterhead. Busoni and
          other musicians also stayed there.</p>
        

      </div>
